ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: CS 522 is a HARD course. But I think it is a fun course to take but also takes up most of your time.
Yes, I am a fellow student. I will recommend it.
Yes. It is a really good course, but I will also remind them the workload as well:)
Yes, but only if he or she wants to learn very serious hacking techniques in low-level system programming.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: From this course I learnt a lot about the Operating Systems. But I am not sure its influence on my research.

Since I did not take OS or OS related course before, this course basically gives me a big picture of OS in terms of computer system level. However, I have still do not quite understand some parts of the OS which I will learn my self later after the course.
Extremely useful for me to understand the computer system; valuable in my future job as a software engineer.
